Name: Double Cramel Frapuccino
Description: A wonderful coffee to work with, its almond and caramel notes are perfectly balanced by the bright, fruity yum of Los Ancestros.

Name: White Chocolate Mocha Frapaccino
Description: Sweet, syrupy and delicious with notes of chocolate-covered cherry and blueberry.

Name: Iced Cafe Latte
Description: Red apple flows into delightful milk chocolate and orange notes that goes dreamily with, or without milk.

Name: White Chocolate Mocha
Description: Best enjoyed all day every day, expect a creamy pecan texture sprinkled with bits of red grape and fig.

Name: Iced Caramel Macchiato
Description: Fresh, juicy and oh so delightful Aricha is an Ethiopian must-taste.

Name: Hot Caramel Macchiato
Description: Delightfully balanced, apple and macadamia notes are highlighted by a honeysuckle sweetness.

Name: Green Tea
Description: Delightful all the way through, peach swims in caramel and custard.

Name: Coffe Mix
Description: Ranking high on our must-try list is La Bolsa from Guatemala.
